Package org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.surveyreports

package org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.surveyreports
Property beans used on the Open Survey Framework interfaces.
  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties
    These beans describe the core properties that are passed to the server to create and update metadata.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AnnotationExtensionProperties
    AnnotationExtensionProperties is used to link a new annotation to an existing annotation.
    AnnotationProperties
    AnnotationProperties is used to record information gleaned from a survey action service.
    AnnotationReviewProperties
    AnnotationReviewProperties is used to review an annotation from a survey report.
    AssociatedAnnotationProperties
    AssociatedAnnotationProperties is used to link a new annotation to the element it describes.
    ClassificationAnnotationProperties
    ClassificationAnnotationProperties recommends classifications for either an asset or a data field.
    DataClassAnnotationProperties
    DataClassAnnotationProperties recommends a data class that potentially matches this data field.
    DataClassMatchProperties
    DataClassMatchProperties is used to link an annotation from a data class and identify how closely it matches.
    DataFieldAnnotationProperties
    DataFieldAnnotationProperties is a common base class for annotations that are attached to a data field.
    DiscoveredSchemaTypeProperties
    DiscoveredSchemaTypeProperties is used to link an annotation from a survey report to schema type.
    FingerprintAnnotationProperties
    FingerprintAnnotationProperties describes properties that describe a fingerprint that captures the characteristics of a data source in a single value.
    QualityAnnotationProperties
    QualityAnnotationProperties records a quality assessment of the data.
    RelationshipAdviceAnnotationProperties
    RelationshipAdviceAnnotationProperties is used to record a recommendation that a new relationship should be made from this data field to another object in the open metadata types.
    ReportedAnnotationProperties
    ReportedAnnotationProperties is used to link a new annotation to the survey report representing the survey that created the annotation.
    RequestForActionAnnotationProperties
    RequestForActionAnnotationProperties is used to record an issue that has been discovered.
    RequestForActionTargetProperties
    RequestForActionTargetProperties identifies the properties of an RequestForActionTarget relationship.
    ResourceMeasureAnnotationProperties
    DataSourceMeasurementAnnotation describes properties that describe the characteristics of the data source as a whole.
    ResourcePhysicalStatusAnnotationProperties
    DataSourceMeasurementAnnotation describes properties that describe the physical characteristics of a data source.
    ResourceProfileAnnotationProperties
    DataProfileAnnotation holds properties that describe the characteristics of a specific field within a data source.
    ResourceProfileDataProperties
    ResourceProfileDataProperties is used to link an annotation from a survey report to an asset that describes the profile data location, for the situation where the profile data is stored outside the metadata repository.
    ResourceProfileLogAnnotationProperties
    DataProfileLogAnnotation is an annotation that is used when the profile data generated is too big to store in the metadata server and has been located in log files instead.
    SchemaAnalysisAnnotationProperties
    SchemaAnalysisAnnotationProperties is used to describe the results of reviewing the structure of the content of an asset.
    SemanticAnnotationProperties
    SemanticAnnotationProperties provides a recommendation as to the likely meaning of data.
    SurveyReportProperties
    SurveyReportProperties describes the properties for a survey report.
